o december   it operated with a substantially different investment strategy specifically it invested primarily in the common stocks and other equity securities of global largecap growth companies and could invest no more than  of its assets in emerging markets securities top  holdings   month end as of  quarter end as of  holdings sector  of net assets samsung electronics co ltd pfd nonvoting information technology  tencent holdings ltd information technology  alibaba group holding ltd sponsored adr information technology  naspers limited class n consumer discretionary  jdcom inc sponsored adr class a consumer discretionary  hdfc bank limited financials  taiwan semiconductor manufacturing co ltd information technology  pt bank rakyat indonesia persero tbk class b financials  ping an insurance group company of china ltd class h financials  cp all public co ltdalien mkt consumer staples  top  total  holdings sector  of net assets samsung electronics co ltd pfd nonvoting information technology  tencent holdings ltd information technology  alibaba group holding ltd sponsored adr information technology  naspers limited class n consumer discretionary  jdcom inc sponsored adr class a consumer discretionary  hdfc bank limited financials  taiwan semiconductor manufacturing co ltd information technology  pt bank rakyat indonesia persero tbk class b financials  ping an insurance group company of china ltd class h financials  cp all public co ltdalien mkt consumer staples  top  total  view all holdings these are not recommendations to buy or sell any security sectors and holdings may vary performance attributionq  estimated performance attribution by sectorq  estimated performance attribution by country sector weightings  as of  sector  of net assets financials  information technology  consumer discretionary  industrials  health care  consumer staples  real estate  telecommunication services  utilities  materials  cash  country weightings  as of  country  of net assets ■ china 